imdb.plot outline: A variety/reality show in which four celebrity dads return home each week to raise their kids by themselves over a 48 hour period window(without the help of their wives that usually do this). Hilarity and touching moments ensue as the fathers go through the ups and downs of being the daily life of being a parent.
